{"tid":1676404,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"譚仔事件新發現","createTime":"2019-10-26T12:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T12:44:09.000Z","uid":308377,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"af21942d5f7fda364c05122052b1ba4fe5a12bfe","tid":1676404,"uid":308377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:16:11.000Z","msg":"譚仔的確比日資收購左<br />\n但丸龜股份下子公司（即東利多）後來買左比heyi group holding limited<br />\n尼個係事實，官網有寫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kBVDi4n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkBVDi4n.png&h=188eb58e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.toridoll.com/cc/company/history.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toridoll.com%2Fcc%2Fcompany%2Fhistory.php&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=a1a9d850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.toridoll.com/cc/company/history.php</a><br />\n見到各大社交媒體話大家炒車<br />\n小弟好奇心起search 左好耐尼間heyi <br />\n然後發現左一個日本食物介紹網有記錄<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZP1gR7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZP1gR7.png&h=0c757fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foodrink.co.jp/sp/detail.php?blog_id=4&amp;entry_id=712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foodrink.co.jp%2Fsp%2Fdetail.php%3Fblog_id%3D4%26entry_id%3D712&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=7905633e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foodrink.co.jp/sp/detail.php?blog_id=4&amp;entry_id=712</a><br />\n以下係內文翻譯<br />\n<br />\n將Toridor Co.，Ltd.的全資子公司Torita Holding Co.，Ltd.（代表高田濱田，香港）出售給合益集團控股有限公司，合益集團控股有限公司在中國經營著2,000家連鎖酒店，如漢庭酒店。 與此同時，上海和北京的香港子公司也將成為合一集團的一部分。 來自各個領域的有影響力的人加入了Torita Holding Co.，Ltd.的管理團隊，以構建更加完善的系統。 選擇本地化而不是自己的發展。<br />\n<br />\n而漢庭酒店母公司即華住集團創辦人乃是季琦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iqCx75i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiqCx75i.png&h=4ffb1854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然信不信譚仔係中資由你<br />\n而he yi 係咪華住企下完全check.唔到<br />\n只知華住企下有好多中丶港丶澳丶美嘅子公司<br />\n<br />\n唔好學我，我真係太得閒先去尋根尋fact check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果大家都覺怪可以幫推討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e784a677a71efb85ba607eb5c6ef7c3a74b61601","tid":1676404,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"唔係好明，簡單總結一下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8933f3084476a0a64d0f1c17d741bd6bf36935d4","tid":1676404,"uid":270563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:22:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1db6b4bd7a1a153f8b19bf543ea631f74beba12","tid":1676404,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:23:43.000Z","msg":"下個發現會唔會係季琦係日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1857885c3dfd91dee67c8c93f45723c22908eaa","tid":1676404,"uid":213747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:24:10.000Z","msg":"新咩發現<br />\n我5個鐘前開post就係解釋<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">東利多控股有限公司</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">東利多和頤有限公司</span>係兩間唔同公司黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[正視聽] 香港譚仔/三哥都係100%日資，<br />\n反而香港丸龜先係63%中資<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675969\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675969</a>"},{"pid":"217b1f801ed4a091c8ebd341e642275a8ec80406","tid":1676404,"uid":104454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:24:20.000Z","msg":"賣股份俾HEYI果間係東利多和頤<br />\n<br />\n而收購譚仔果間係東利多 100%股份由東利多持有<br />\n<br />\n譚仔同中日合資既東利多和頤係冇直接關係<br />\n<br />\n當然你可以話兩間野既母企都係東利多所以東利多奶共既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42dfca338dae2b5fc464ccf256270ea5db398fe2","tid":1676404,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:26:02.000Z","msg":"仲未玩完Fake